<div class="alert alert-info mb-4" role="alert">
    <h4 class="alert-heading"><span class="bi bi-info-circle"></span> About Parameter Resolution</h4>
    <p>
        This sample demonstrates the <strong>Parameter Resolution</strong> feature in Blazing.Mvvm, which enables automatic
        parameter binding between Blazor components (Views) and their ViewModels.
    </p>
    <div class="row mt-3">
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <h6><span class="bi bi-1-circle"></span> View Parameters</h6>
            <p class="small">
                Define parameters in your Blazor component using <code>[Parameter]</code> and 
                <code>[SupplyParameterFromQuery]</code> attributes for query string values.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <h6><span class="bi bi-2-circle"></span> ViewModel Properties</h6>
            <p class="small">
                Mark ViewModel properties with <code>[ViewParameter]</code> to automatically 
                receive values from the View's parameters.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <hr />
    <p class="mb-0">
        <span class="bi bi-lightbulb"></span> <strong>Key Feature:</strong> 
        Supports property name mapping, custom name mapping with <code>[ViewParameter("Name")]</code>, 
        and works seamlessly with <code>[ObservableProperty]</code> from CommunityToolkit.Mvvm.
    </p>
</div>
